{"id": "1235646385479614464", "channel_id": "1235079584047697981", "type": 0, "author_id": "1221463356138061828", "author_name": "lilisi123456", "author_bot": false, "content": "🍟", "timestamp": "2024-05-02T17:37:35.498000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1235079584047697981", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[福袋24]首回合瞬秒癫三13万血潘神", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584"]}
{"id": "1235636090925224098", "channel_id": "1235636090925224098", "type": 0, "author_id": "757961390412660836", "author_name": "crimsonkiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "如题，和讨论区大佬讨论之后做个笔记，方便大家查阅。以后新增角色或启灵估值有变动时，会继续更新。\n\n图鲁 2\n大福袋 1\n红夫人 2\n莉莉 3\n墨菲 2\n旺达 3\n神父 0/2\n24 1\n羊妈 2", "timestamp": "2024-05-02T16:56:41.085000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-18T03:27:52.505000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 17}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1235636090925224098", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［抛砖引玉］「讨论笔记」各限定角色当前最佳CP值启灵<不断更新>", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748", "1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179680056791130", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1235521869382160425", "channel_id": "1235521869382160425", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "計算了24活動收益，收益標準皆以65等級的活動關卡為準。\n\n先說結論，**若需要技能素材，刷第五關，只想要印章和徽章，刷第二關，只想要徽章，則刷第一關。**\n\n調查徽章的收益不易換算，可自行對照，調查徽章兌換一啟靈(2500)，約等於217印章，或79萬金卷。\n\n第五關總掉落高於其他關卡，但由於技能素材兌換價值較低，整體而言第五關的效益只略高第一、二關一些(圖在留言處)。\n\n可看到若共鳴拿滿，相比刷金卷本，收益倍率有1.778倍，高於先前的旺達活動印章或神父活動收益(不算銀芯)。\n沒開滿則視自身情況對照。\n\n使用方法：\n\n可於excel紅字處輸入自帶的限定額外掉落(進活動關前顯示的掉落)，或參考附圖。\n\n24、24命輪、夫人、夫人命輪、活動SR卡，本體各自提供15%掉落，每一啟靈額外提供5%，最高共150%。\n若抽了一張24，和SR命輪拿四張以上，則自帶限定共鳴為45%，以此類推。\n\n活動啟靈給予的每120體力返還20體力，和50%掉落，都已算入表內，若未開啟靈則不建議刷24活動。\n\n有誤煩請指出，我會試著改正。\n\np.s.本篇只計算能無限兌換的部分，有限兌換商品建議全數換完。\n\nUID:100352106", "timestamp": "2024-05-02T09:22:48.547000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-08T02:24:37.732000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1235521869814435911", "filename": "24.xlsx", "content_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet", "size": 12263, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1235521869382160425/1235521869814435911/24.xlsx?ex=69cb9268&is=69ca40e8&hm=2512dc7065a36f8b9162822fd9e4ecc5de7d0cc74988d6fafd166ac20ce03589&"}, {"id": "1235521870535594046", "filename": "0.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 74617, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1235521869382160425/1235521870535594046/0.JPG?ex=69cb9268&is=69ca40e8&hm=e108c445af89d07824c2ebef3ca806b3085177da59879a1408be60f485470a07&"}, {"id": "1235521870779125803", "filename": "50.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 75953, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1235521869382160425/1235521870779125803/50.JPG?ex=69cb9268&is=69ca40e8&hm=b16b3d54d7451ff4d6fb980a1a79c38d9c0826ba0f07726729340f9ba938d746&"}, {"id": "1235521871047430154", "filename": "100.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 73326, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1235521869382160425/1235521871047430154/100.JPG?ex=69cb9268&is=69ca40e8&hm=41244ee8522d24ff1120aa86045d848ab0f024c3101c2a651bac833528ec65f6&"}, {"id": "1235521871332511785", "filename": "150.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 75078, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1235521869382160425/1235521871332511785/150.JPG?ex=69cb9269&is=69ca40e9&hm=a1e313ba52e08df0d5e898cc411bb6a70ca09be58ea63bc73efbfd131b871e2d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1235521869382160425", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "24活動掉落收益計算", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
