{"id": "1235639476127137833", "channel_id": "1235544468686372874", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.驱散技能对敌方使用  可以破除嘲讽效果和护盾效果，但这一技能机制目前十分稀缺，仅以下角色拥有:\n為什麼這裡沒有汀", "timestamp": "2024-05-02T17:10:08.180000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-02T17:10:18.475000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1160794721615093831"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1235546815688867842", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1235544468686372874", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［PVP］角色实战作用统计——非输出篇", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130"]}
